ZH: 我们明天会面讨论项目进度。
EN: We will meet tomorrow to discuss the project progress.

ZH: 他们上周末会面商讨合作事宜。
EN: They met last weekend to discuss cooperation matters.

ZH: 我们已经安排好了下周的会面时间。
EN: We have already scheduled the meeting time for next week.

ZH: 请将您的建议提前告知，以便我们做好会面准备。
EN: Please inform us of your suggestions in advance so we can prepare for the meeting.

ZH: 我们需要召开一次紧急会面解决这个问题。
EN: We need to hold an emergency meeting to resolve this issue.

ZH: 设定一个预算在我们的会面议程中。
EN: Include a budget setting in our meeting agenda.

ZH: 请确认下周二早上九点的会面时间是否可以。
EN: Please confirm if the meeting time at 9 am next Tuesday is okay.

ZH: 由于时间冲突，我们不得不取消了明天的会面。
EN: Due to scheduling conflicts, we have to cancel tomorrow's meeting.

ZH: 我们需要安排一个视频会面与跨国合作伙伴进行讨论。
EN: We need to schedule a video meeting to discuss with our international partners.

ZH: 请确保会面地点和时间不会发生变化。
EN: Please ensure that the meeting location and time remain unchanged.

ZH: 我们的会面已经延期到下周。
EN: Our meeting has been postponed until next week.

ZH: 会面时请准备好所有必要的资料。
EN: Please have all necessary documents ready for the meeting.

ZH: 请确认您收到了会面通知。
EN: Please confirm that you have received the meeting invitation.

ZH: 会面结束后会发放会议纪要。
EN: Meeting minutes will be distributed after the meeting.

ZH: 请您提前安排好交通，以免迟到会面。
EN: Please arrange your transportation in advance to avoid being late for the meeting.

ZH: 会面时请您务必戴上口罩。
EN: Please wear a mask during the meeting.

ZH: 我们计划下周六与客户会面商讨新合作项目。
EN: We plan to meet with the client next Saturday to discuss new cooperation projects.

ZH: 会面地点定在市中心的咖啡厅。
EN: The meeting location is set at a downtown café.

ZH: 下次会面将在视频会议的形式进行。
EN: The next meeting will be conducted in the form of a video conference.

ZH: 会面时请尽量不要打断他人发言。
EN: Please try not to interrupt others during the meeting.
